Dear GODI Packagers,

If you're packaging a project that's gone to the trouble of writing
ocamldoc documentation and example code, please do generate the
documentation and install those example files.  It's a bit silly that
after installing a library with GODI you still need to download the
source tarball and navigate its build system just to get the API docs.

